values: Yiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiipeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeee I am done with #2 of 4 acounting classes.  I hate accounting and have a lot more respect for the profession after taking these classes.  I now know why accountans get paid so much.

Well it has been a while since my last and only post.  Since then something has given.  I quit my job.  Haluhlooyer.  Now I am stressed because I don't have any of my own money any more.  I know, I know, I'd complain if I was hung with a new rope.
My God I can't take this anymore!!!!!!!!  What was I thinking!?  Working full time and go to school full time? And I have five to six years left!  Am I insane?  Something has got to give.
